{"_id":"5RB13H0P7WvxVDBr","name":"Pilotage","type":"skill","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/skills/airplane.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_z90ozbl8e5a","path":"Skills","color":"#8c160f"}},"system":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core\">\n<p>Pilotage permet d&rsquo;utiliser tous les types d&rsquo;appareils a&eacute;riens ou spatiaux comme les avions, h&eacute;licopt&egrave;res, jet-packs ou vaisseaux. Vous trouverez les r&egrave;gles sur les Poursuites au Chapitre Quatre. Un personnage avec une Capacit&eacute; inn&eacute;e &agrave; voler (avec des ailes, par exemple) utilise la Comp&eacute;tence Athl&eacute;tisme.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"attribute":"agility","isCoreSkill":false,"die":{"sides":4,"modifier":0},"wild-die":{"sides":6},"source":""},"ownership":{"default":0,"7ntJSLixH2Phv2jV":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.0.2","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1664231520822,"lastModifiedBy":"ROoEjeqzfM4eLJ4v"}}
